{"tid":1197953,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T06:08:08.000Z","uid":190319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"efa009fd8b34a6a503978d20dc364277072e7e21","tid":1197953,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:01:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iyYsEyo-QTM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiyYsEyo-QTM&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=15cda367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iyYsEyo-QTM</a> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以試下接觸下當今既問題！<br />\n<br />\n一個人力量係微不足道；<br />\n但一群人力量就係力大無窮。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再比藉口自己，放棄成個香港，係時候企出黎，維護自己既家，唔好再比班無良政府繼續改變我地既思想，影響我地既下一代。<br />\n<br />\n只要香港人齊心協力，相信能夠利用國際力量，去改變、去維護自己既家。<br />\n<br />\n6月12號，大家再次企出黎，打壓無良政府，抗惡法。<br />\n<br />\n最緊要個句，大家記住安全至上。"},{"pid":"f1ea1ce29515a5266a686548e510661391a62017","tid":1197953,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"撞"},{"pid":"53dfe25a05de783206fdf0b5f13d341c401db1af","tid":1197953,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e717ac6ad1c9630166590d551c8a163b50f08a13","tid":1197953,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"比多啲人知道 香港發生緊既問題"},{"pid":"1d34635a1549d49c013d029d40850e2727db7e29","tid":1197953,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:04:14.000Z","msg":"推比多啲人知"},{"pid":"b5e07feb2828e6b2f5e87aa99df70510fe738a74","tid":1197953,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"香港人 加油 維護自己既屋企"},{"pid":"267286d989361c6207cd6cd2c81b9c516f344cc1","tid":1197953,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:05:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66cf91c570373a53d9767df5cf5be2d872d6a5b7","tid":1197953